state.code:
sequenceDiagram
    User->>+Application: Search and Hit Enter
    Application->>+Server: getSearchResultsList(query)
    Server->>+Question: Questions.find(word)
    Question->>+Question: Questions.Reduce(word)
    Question-->>-Server: questionSearchResults

    Server->>+Tag: .filter(tag)
    Tag-->>-Server: tagSearchResults
    Server-->>-Application: filteredSearchResults
